metadata.name: CryptoPunks Art Club #1
metadata.description: **PUBLIC MINT IS CURRENTLY LIVE at https://cryptopunksartclub.art.**  Mint for only .12 ETH per painting while minting is still open.  *Become a Punk.*  As an Art Club member, you can own any of the 10,000 CryptoPunks, thoughtfully recreated into unique AI-generated oil paintings. Only one painting will be minted for each CryptoPunk, and 24 distinct AI-models have been applied across the collection, to help create value for the owner of every individual ERC-721 token. Each mint of CryptoPunk Art will be eligible for future drops of specially designed frames to highlight your fine Punk art.
